// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3579 — Mass File Rename (noescape)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 60ba4884-710b-5299-992c-f0ac14582424

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
